summary: So I was re-watching the live read of “McMystery at McDuck McManor!” and, honestly, the moment when Toks Olagundoye (Beakley’s...
body: So I was re-watching the live read of “McMystery at McDuck McManor!” and, honestly, the moment when Toks Olagundoye (Beakley’s VA) tries to give David Tennant his itinerary and David Tennant tosses it away is such a Beakley and Scrooge thing.  You cannot convince me that that would’ve never happened in canon.

reblog.comment: So I was re-watching the live read of “McMystery at McDuck McManor!” and, honestly, the moment when Toks Olagundoye (Beakley’s VA) tries to give David Tennant his itinerary and David Tennant tosses it away is such a Beakley and Scrooge thing.  You cannot convince me that that would’ve never happened in canon.

trail.content: So I was re-watching the live read of “McMystery at McDuck McManor!” and, honestly, the moment when Toks Olagundoye (Beakley’s VA) tries to give David Tennant his itinerary and David Tennant tosses it away is such a Beakley and Scrooge thing.  You cannot convince me that that would’ve never happened in canon.

blog.title: Everything Will Be All Right In The End...

summary: I had such a great weekend at the London film and comic con!! Met so many wonderful people who made the experience all that more...
caption:
I had such a great weekend at the London film and comic con!! Met so many wonderful people who made the experience all that more fantastic!

I also got some autographs from David Bradley, James Callis, Paul McGann (who disclosed some information about his character in Holby which was interesting) and Ingrid Oliver’s autograph who remembered me the next day when I went for the photo op. She even gave me a hug which was so sweet and lovely!! But Peter grabbing my hand and saying will you be my companion was just ahh no words. Meeting David Tennant I still can’t believe though. When he got announced on the Saturday the atmosphere was just amazing!!

All of it feels surreal but it’s definitely made my year (along with meeting Judi back in May)🙈
